import React from "react";
import {
  MDBCarousel,
  MDBCarouselItem,
  MDBCol,
  MDBIcon,
  MDBTypography,
  MDBContainer,
  MDBRow,
} from "mdb-react-ui-kit";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <MDBContainer className="py-5">
      <MDBCarousel showControls dark>
        <MDBCarouselItem className="active">
          <MDBContainer>
            <MDBRow className="text-center">
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="mb-5 mb-md-0">
                {/* Content for the first carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the second carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the third carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
          </MDBContainer>
        </MDBCarouselItem>
        <MDBCarouselItem>
          <MDBContainer>
            <MDBRow className="text-center">
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="mb-5 mb-md-0">
                {/* Content for the fourth carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the fifth carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the sixth carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
          </MDBContainer>
        </MDBCarouselItem>
        <MDBCarouselItem>
          <MDBContainer>
            <MDBRow className="text-center">
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="mb-5 mb-md-0">
                {/* Content for the seventh carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the eighth carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
              <MDBCol lg="4" className="d-none d-lg-block">
                {/* Content for the ninth carousel item */}
              </MDBCol>
            </MDBRow>
          </MDBContainer>
        </MDBCarouselItem>
      </MDBCarousel>
    </MDBContainer>
  );
}
